                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#99ra">99ra</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘጐይታና፡ ገብረ፡ ማርያም፡ ስመ፡ አቡሁ፡
